{
  "stem": "12768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we were ready-- after my mother had been taken by the Germans, we were trying to find out, of course, where they had taken her.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the only thing that the chauffeur could say was that they were going to be taken to Copenhagen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had our friends that was trying, the Madsens, to see if they could find out through some of their family in Copenhagen what was happening.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said that Minnie was going to be taken to Germany, and that was all we knew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then my father had called from Copenhagen and said, I'm ready.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How am I going to get there?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we told my father to take the train from Copenhagen to Helsingor, and of course disguise himself a little bit to not look like everybody else, and just look like the average Joe citizen, you know, this-- doing some business, have a little valise, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my father took the train, and nobody bothered asking him any questions or anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had bought a ticket, and he went on the train and came to the city of Helsingor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like I say, that is 12 miles-- or 12 kilometers, which is about eight miles from our city of Hornbaek.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we figured, how are we going to get him up here?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So somebody suggested that I go on bicycle, because I was the least suspicious character.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I went to my friend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was-- his father was a blacksmith in our-- in the summer town of Hornbaek.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I borrowed my friend's clothes, blacksmith clothes what's is all greasy, oily, dirty clothes, and I had a blacksmith hat on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I took the one bicycle and rode with another one next to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
